tributes like title, category, and status.\n\n\n**Mapping UI Components**\n\nI'm now identifying the key UI components for displaying document data within the application. I'm focusing on the `WorkspaceCard` and `DocumentsErrorState` components to map them with API data and implement error handling. I'm paying attention to how these components handle loading states and error messages.\n\n\n"}}
